Package com.sixbank.notificationlibrary.shared.dto.response

Class NotificationResponse

java.lang.Object
com.sixbank.notificationlibrary.shared.dto.response.NotificationResponse
public class NotificationResponse extends Object
DTO class representing the response of a notification operation. This class is typically used when returning notification information to API clients.
